{"tid":38292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新水炮車設6水炮全面覆蓋　可混入催淚煙水","createTime":"2016-12-13T23:11:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T01:26:33.000Z","uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0956935c67f29fa32ed43c9fe17fb2375773c1","tid":38292,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:11:04.000Z","msg":"[img]<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/photo/bkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_01p.jpg[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_01p.jpg%5B%2Fimg&d=KCL0DCm18s2c8hNvA4Vb%2BHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=8a20e5fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/photo/bkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_01p.jpg[/img</a><br />\n香港前年爆發佔領行動後，警方計劃斥資2700萬港元購入3架俗稱「水炮車」的群眾管理車輛，早前已完成招標程序，由香港一間公司中標，前期生產工序將於法國進行，之後回港進行後期組裝。據了解，3架車上將共有6支水炮，同時設6部閉路電視同步錄影，確保使用過程符合安全守則；至於能否於明年七‧一遊行20周年前付運到港，要視乎生產進度。<br />\n<br />\n警隊去年12月就3架水炮車進行招標，最終由香港公司仁孚行中標。據悉，警方經過細心研究，將安裝2大4小共6支水炮，設有3個水缸負責供水，水力與之前構思大致相若。<br />\n<br />\n根據當時的招標文件，2支主炮每分鐘射水最少1200公升，水壓最少有1000kPa(千帕)，射程50米，水炮需能左右轉動180度，以達至360度的全方位覆蓋率。另外，水炮的角度需可調校至上仰60度、下調40度；水炮車除可噴水及噴泡外，亦可混入催淚煙水劑以及顏料噴出。<br />\n<br />\n車上另會安裝6部閉路電視並進行錄影，確保使用過程中符合安全守則，以便一旦有任何爭議，亦有片段作證據。雖然3架水炮車是參考歐洲設計，前期生產工序亦會於法國進行，但絕非現時法國警方使用的型號，而是因應香港環境度身訂造，體積限制為不可超過7.8米長、2.5米闊及4.1米高，可載4人，全車每年可走2萬公里，最少可運作9年。<br />\n<br />\n對於有警隊管理層早前透露，希望3架水炮車可於明年七‧一前在港使用，以應付一旦出現佔領行動等大型人群示威，但最終情況，仍須視乎生產進度。警方一直強調，警隊引入水炮車是多一個選擇，不代表放棄使用催淚彈，要按實際情況而定。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/photo/bkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_03b.jpg[img][/img][/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_03b.jpg%5Bimg%5D%5B%2Fimg%5D%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=KCL0DCm18s2c8hNvA4Vb%2BHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=86913a91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/photo/bkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_03b.jpg[img][/img][/img]</a>"},{"pid":"58c97b5ad69c474b075c28751d2a9147565df367","tid":38292,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/photo/bkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_01p.jpg&h=f94952e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/photo/bkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_03b.jpg[img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_03b.jpg%5Bimg%5D&d=KCL0DCm18s2c8hNvA4Vb%2BHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1d63176f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/photo/bkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_03b.jpg[img]</a>"},{"pid":"71c02a9c11c110cee03c0e3faafab444bbd584f2","tid":38292,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/photo/bkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_03b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161214000114773-1214_00822_001_03b.jpg&h=e9214c33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65776b2c9cf712a0292364a6ba1dca191ee797b7","tid":38292,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:16:06.000Z","msg":"我又諗起Saving Private Ryan最後一段用過的&quot;土製&quot;sticky bomb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15e8556244a74bfe9297147a834435943292992","tid":38292,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T23:19:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},